		<label>Muramasa Sol</label>
		<description>This is an ultra-rare artifact sword, reputedly the creation of legendary swordsmith Sengo Muramasa. Shrouded in myth, Muramasa's blades have a reputation for being cursed and demonic in nature. This blade, the Muramasa Sol, is true to the legends - it is nearly weightless, has a wicked cutting ability rivaling that of ultratech monoblades, and bestows powerful boons upon its wielder. The inner workings of the blade are a mystery. Whether it is actually a 4000-year old sword that hails from the Old Earth, the creation of an advanced glitterworld smith, or a persona-infused gift from a mad machine god is unknown.</description>
